Paper: hep-th/9904039

Date: 1999-04-06

Title: A Regularization Scheme for the AdS/CFT Correspondence

Authors: W. Mueck and K.S. Viswanathan

Comments: 5 pages, uses amsmath, amssymb packages, v2

Journal-ref: JHEP 9907 (1999) 018

The prescription of the AdS/CFT correspondence is refined by using aregularization procedure, which makes is possible to calculate the divergentlocal terms in the CFT two-point function. We present the procedure for theexample of the scalar field.